sql: SELECT COURSEalias0.NAME , COURSEalias0.NUMBER FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 , COURSE AS COURSEalias1 , PROGRAM_COURSE AS PROGRAM_COURSEalias0 WHERE COURSEalias1.COURSE_ID NOT IN ( SELECT COURSE_PREREQUISITEalias0.PRE_COURSE_ID FROM COURSE_PREREQUISITE AS COURSE_PREREQUISITEalias0 WHERE COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSE_PREREQUISITEalias0.COURSE_ID ) AND COURSEalias1.DEPARTMENT = "EECS" AND COURSEalias1.NUMBER = 281 AND PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.CATEGORY = "ULCS" AND PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID ;
